beer.beer_description:
With a 100% Australian hop bill this beer was unleashed to showcase the world-class hops we grow locally.

A well balanced but firmly bitter fruit bowl of pineapple, mango and apricot.

Hops: Enigma, Ella, Vic Secret

Replaces the Australian Psycho IPA with a tweaked recipe.
